# Strapi Schema Overview

This rule provides an overview of all schemas (content types) in the Infinity Backend Strapi project.

## Content Types

- [Product](mdc:src/api/product/content-types/product/schema.json) - Product catalog items
- [Product Variation](mdc:src/api/product-variation/content-types/product-variation/schema.json) - Variations of products
- [Product Category](mdc:src/api/product-category/content-types/product-category/schema.json) - Categories for products
- [Product Tag](mdc:src/api/product-tag/content-types/product-tag/schema.json) - Tags for products
- [Product Review](mdc:src/api/product-review/content-types/product-review/schema.json) - Reviews for products
- [Product FAQ](mdc:src/api/product-faq/content-types/product-faq/schema.json) - FAQs for products
- [Product Size Helper](mdc:src/api/product-size-helper/content-types/product-size-helper/schema.json) - Size helpers for products
- [Cart](mdc:src/api/cart/content-types/cart/schema.json) - Shopping cart
- [Cart Item](mdc:src/api/cart-item/content-types/cart-item/schema.json) - Items in shopping cart
- [Order](mdc:src/api/order/content-types/order/schema.json) - Customer orders
- [Order Item](mdc:src/api/order-item/content-types/order-item/schema.json) - Items in customer orders
- [Local User](mdc:src/api/local-user/content-types/local-user/schema.json) - User authentication
- [Local User Info](mdc:src/api/local-user-info/content-types/local-user-info/schema.json) - User profile information
- [Local User Address](mdc:src/api/local-user-address/content-types/local-user-address/schema.json) - User addresses
- [Local User Wallet](mdc:src/api/local-user-wallet/content-types/local-user-wallet/schema.json) - User wallet
- [Shipping](mdc:src/api/shipping/content-types/shipping/schema.json) - Shipping methods
- [Payment Gateway](mdc:src/api/payment-gateway/content-types/payment-gateway/schema.json) - Payment gateway options

